diers.  So here are a few of my ideas for types:<br /><br />Leaders/ sworn members of the Faith:  a septon, a septa, a silent sister, and a begging brother, a brown brother, a poor fellow, a warrior's son, even a knight as knighthood involves a religious ceremony.<br /><br />Leaders/ sworn members of other religions:  greenseer, Drowned God priest, a member of the Dosh Khaleen, a Red Priest/ Priestess, Priest of the Many-Faced God.<br /><br />Wildings: spearwife, a giant, a Thenn, a Hornfoot, a cave dweller, a nightrunner, a walrus man, a clan member of the ice rivers.<br /><br />Other general ideas for these characters are:  maester, alchemist, Master at Arms etc.<br />","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"9 years ago","ctime":"February 28 2008, 03:18:40 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"Actually not related to this subject - miniature ideas","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://cochick.livejournal.com/","striked":1,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"cochick","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"cochick","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://cochick.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"cochick","ctime_ts":1204168720,"tracked":0}]}